Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:27.38,Akizuki,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiccyan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:27.38,Akizuki,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs13\pos(315,335)}ちっちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.64,0:00:30.39,Akizuki,,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊 哪有这么一号人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.39,0:00:32.39,Akizuki,,0000,0000,0000,,一大早的糊里糊涂的可不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.40,0:00:33.89,Akizuki,,0000,0000,0000,,但对真来说这还真稀罕哎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.89,0:00:35.50,Kikuchi,,0000,0000,0000,,不 看那里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.28,0:00:37.55,Otonashi,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.73,0:00:39.30,Otonashi,,0000,0000,0000,,来 请喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:43.40,Otonashi,,0000,0000,0000,,工作方面怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.36,0:00:48.49,Akizuki,,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没看到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.49,0:00:50.66,Kikuchi,,0000,0000,0000,,面对现实吧 律子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.67,0:00:56.63,Kikuchi,,0000,0000,0000,,是小鸟小姐捡来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.64,0:00:59.19,Otonashi,,0000,0000,0000,,看她在路边挨冻太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.21,0:01:00.11,Otonashi,,0000,0000,0000,,所以就
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:02.58,Kikuchi,,0000,0000,0000,,名字是……Chiccyan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:02.58,Kikuchi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs13\pos(365,335)}ちっちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.67,0:01:05.01,Otonashi,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因为跟律子小姐太像了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.16,0:01:07.01,Kikuchi,,0000,0000,0000,,但是没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.02,0:01:08.46,Kikuchi,,0000,0000,0000,,连工作都交给她
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.51,0:01:09.53,Otonashi,,0000,0000,0000,,这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.54,0:01:11.86,Otonashi,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子其实头脑非常好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.04,0:01:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一模一样吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.52,0:01:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是新的迷你偶像 Chiccyan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.52,0:01:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs13\pos(405,335)}ちっちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.04,0:01:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是小鸟小姐捡来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.81,0:01:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,头脑非常灵光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.40,0:01:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能胜任事务所的全部脑力工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.89,0:01:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也很擅长照顾人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是迷你偶像们的大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.77,0:01:50.10,Otonashi,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.11,0:01:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对于没用的大人也能狠狠地教训
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.33,0:01:54.95,Otonashi,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:01:56.80,Otonashi,,0000,0000,0000,,迷你偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:01:56.80,Otonashi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs13\pos(320,335)}ぷちます!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 律子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.50,0:02:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音无小姐的会议文件好像不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:04.08,Akizuki,,0000,0000,0000,,骗人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.57,0:02:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了 只能赶紧去找了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.69,0:02:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太感谢了 得救了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 喂 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.37,0:02:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来很不擅长对付P
